title: How to transfer data from Smart Switch on my Mac to my Google Pixel phone?
content:
I want to transfer data from my old Samsung phone to my new Google Pixel. However I lost my old phone, but have the backup data on my IMac.

I used Smart Switch to backup my Samsung to my Mac, and so the data is on there. How do I transfer from Smart Switch to my new phone?
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 2
